high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the end of the black couch, walk to the gray door and head right to the white desk.
Pick up the box of tissues near the end of the white desk.
Turn left, walk to the black couch, hang a left towards the wall, and head right to the tall lamp in the corner near the wall.
anns.task_desc: Examine a box of tissues by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and go halfway along the sofa, then turn right and cross the room to the door, then turn left when you reach the door.
Pick up the tissue box that is in front of you.
Turn to your left and cross the room to the lamp at the left end of the sofa, then hold the box up between you and the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a tissue box in the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Move to the TV stand facing the box of tissues
pick up the box of tissues sitting on top of the TV stand
Carry the box of tissues to the floor lamp next to the grey sofa
Turn on the floor lamp to the left of the sofa
anns.task_desc: Carry a box of tissues while turning on a floor lamp
